data.description: LOCATION LOCATION LOCATION! This lot is for sale along with the one next to it at 2504 Race Street for a total of over .4 acres. Both lots are zoned B-1 for duplexes, but which also allows for two properties per lot. Current main house is leased out and the two houses in the back could easily be fixed up and leased out. Or the lot can be cleared and up to four houses can be constructed. Surrounding properties have been re-zoned for multi-use so even a small apartment or condo complex could be developed. Perfect opportunity for an investment in the booming Riverside District. Views of Downtown, the Trinity River and so much more. The surrounding area is being revitalized and property values are on the rise. Come see the amazing potential of this property located on Race Street right between Oakhurst and Sylvania. Listing is being sold with MLS number MLS number 20448204
